Subject: Re: [T2] Heater blower motor switch

The blue wire connects to the blue alternator warning light wire that
comes off the voltage regulator if memory serves correctly. This
prevents the fan from running anytime the alt warning light is on.

http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/info/wiringt2.php

J14 is the relay. Follow the wires from there.

